ctx: intros A e k x a H.
exceptions.exn: In environment A : Type e : env A k, x : nat a : A H : length (insert x a e) <= k + 1 The term "length_empty A (S k)" has type "length (empty A) <= S k" while it is expected to have type "k + 1 <= ?p" (cannot unify "length (empty A)" and "k + 1").

original: intros A e k x a H. apply (le_trans _ _ _ H (length_empty A (S k))).
